text: Dolichestola vittipennis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1948. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Dolichestola vittipennis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==External links== ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1948
